sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: Text Detection Request

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP | No TLS | No Auth
    Note right of Detector: Request Body:<br/>{ contents: [{ content: "text..." }],<br/>  detector_params: {<br/>    regex: ["email", "ssn",<br/>            "credit-card"] or<br/>    ["custom-pattern"] } }

    alt Built-in Pattern (email, ssn, credit-card)
        Note right of Detector: Lookup named regex<br/>from built-in map
    else Custom Pattern
        Note right of Detector: Compile regex from<br/>detector_params.regex string
    end

    Detector->>Detector: Execute regex against<br/>each content string

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: HTTP 200 JSON Response
    Note left of Orchestrator: Response Body:<br/>[{ detection: "pii-email",<br/>   detection_type: "pii",<br/>   score: 1.0,<br/>   evidence: [{<br/>     start: 10, end: 30,<br/>     text: "user@example.com"<br/>   }] }]

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Orchestrator->>Detector: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 "healthy"
